\c 12
\s UShishaki uhlasela ilizwe lakoJuda
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi uRehobhowamu eseqinise umbuso, eseziqinisile\x + 12.13. 11.17. 26.16.\x*, watshiya umlayo weN\nd kosi\nd*, loIsrayeli wonke laye\x + 12.5. 1 Kho. 14.22-24.\x*.
\p
\v 2 Kwasekusithi ngomnyaka wesihlanu wenkosi uRehobhowamu, uShishaki inkosi yeGibhithe wenyuka wamelana leJerusalema, ngoba babephambukile eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + 12.9. 1 Kho. 14.25. 1 Kho. 11.40.\x*,
\v 3 elezinqola ezingamakhulu alitshumi lambili labagadi bamabhiza abazinkulungwane ezingamatshumi ayisithupha; labantu babengelakubalwa abeza laye bephuma eGibhithe, amaLibiya\x + 16.8. Dan. 11.43. Nah. 3.9.\x*, amaSukhi, lamaEthiyophiya\x + 16.8. Dan. 11.43. Nah. 3.9.\x*.
\v 4 Wasethumba imizi ebiyelweyo eyayingeyakoJuda weza eJerusalema\x + 11.5-12.\x*.
\p
\v 5 UShemaya umprofethi wasefika kuRehobhowamu\x + 11.2. 1 Kho. 12.22.\x* lezikhulu zakoJuda ezazibuthene eJerusalema ngenxa kaShishaki, wathi kubo: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Lina lingilahlile, ngakho lami ngililahlele esandleni sikaShishaki\x + 15.2.\x*.
\v 6 Iziphathamandla zakoIsrayeli kanye lenkosi basebezithoba\x + 21.2.\x* bathi: IN\nd kosi\nd* ilungile\x + Eks. 9.27.\x*.
\v 7 IN\nd kosi\nd* isibona ukuthi bazithobile\x + 7.14. 12.12. 1 Kho. 21.29. Jak. 4.10.\x*, ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* lafika kuShemaya lisithi: Bazithobile; kangiyikubabhubhisa, kodwa ngizabanika isilinganiso sokukhululwa, lolaka lwami kaluyikuthululelwa eJerusalema ngesandla sikaShishaki\x + 34.25.\x*.
\v 8 Kodwa bazakuba zinceku zakhe ukuze bazi inkonzo yami lenkonzo yemibuso yamazwe\x + Dute. 28.47,48. Isa. 26.13.\x*.
\v 9 Ngakho uShishaki inkosi yeGibhithe wenyukela eJerusalema, wathatha okuligugu kwendlu kaJehova lokuligugu kwendlu yenkosi\x + 1 Kho. 14.25-28.\x*, wathatha konke; wathatha lezihlangu zegolide uSolomoni ayezenzile\x + 9.16.\x*.
\v 10 Inkosi uRehobhowamu yasisenza izihlangu zethusi endaweni yazo, ya\add zi\add*nikela ngaphansi kwesandla senduna zabalindi ababegcina umnyango wendlu yenkosi.
\v 11 Kwasekusithi lapho inkosi ingena endlini kaJehova bafika abalindi bezithwele, bazibuyisela ekamelweni labalindi.
\v 12 Isizithobile, ulaka lweN\nd kosi\nd* lwaphenduka lwasuka kuyo ukuze inga\add yi\add*bhubhisi ngokuphelelelyo; futhi lakoJuda kwakulezinto ezinhle.
\p
\v 13 Inkosi uRehobhowamu yasiziqinisa eJerusalema, yabusa\x + 12.1. 13.21.\x*. Ngoba uRehobhowamu wayeleminyaka engamatshumi amane lanye lapho esiba yinkosi\x + 1 Kho. 14.21.\x*, wabusa iminyaka elitshumi lesikhombisa eJerusalema, umuzi iN\nd kosi\nd* eyayiwukhethile phakathi kwazo zonke izizwe zakoIsrayeli, ukubeka ibizo layo khona. Lebizo likanina lalinguNahama umAmonikazi\x + 6.6.\x*.
\v 14 Wasesenza okubi ngoba engalungisanga inhliziyo yakhe ukudinga iN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 15 Lendaba zikaRehobhowamu\x + 1 Kho. 14.29-31.\x*, ezokuqala lezokucina\x + 1 Lan. 29.29.\x*, kazibhalwanga yini ezindabeni zikaShemaya umprofethi\x + 1 Kho. 12.22.\x* lezikaIdo\x + 9.29.\x* umboni\x + 2 Sam. 24.11.\x* mayelana lemibhalo yosendo\x + 1 Lan. 5.1,7,17. 9.1.\x*, lezimpi zikaRehobhowamu loJerobhowamu zonke izinsuku?
\v 16 URehobhowamu waselala laboyise, wangcwatshelwa emzini kaDavida. UAbhiya indodana yakhe wasesiba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe.